high_descs: Face the counter in front of you.
Turn right and take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter on your right.
Slice the lettuce in front of you.
Turn left and face the cabinet under the counter in front of you.
Open the cabinet in front of you, place the knife inside then close the cabinet.
Face right and face the counter with the lettuce in front of you.
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the sink on your left.
Wash the lettuce in the sink then take it out.
Turn around and face the fridge on your right.
Place the lettuce in the fridge in front of you and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place clean lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and step forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn left and look down to face the right most cabinet.
Place the knife in the thin corner cabinet.
Turn right to face the sliced lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the sliced lettuce on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the sink.
wash the lettuce slice in the sink and remove it.
Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Place the slice of lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To wash a slice of lettuce and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife to the left of the pan.
Turn around and go across  the room to the counter on the left of the sink.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Go to the cabinet to the right of the stove in the corner.
Put the knife in the cabinet.
Go to the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Move over to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Go to the fridge.
Put the piece of lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of lettuce in the fridge.
